ont-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Manuel Orbegozo/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;总统竞选是最新的戏剧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;保守党藤森庆子在周日的决选后领先出局。随后，随着来自农村地区的选票陆续涌入，她的左翼竞争对手&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/QKJDU9HpsGX00n7CrERgR92BTBfQCappYgP7Divrw0tQqo9FqcIvRf71Y6euD2TOGttYLnbLEMGlzIk2Lv7Jhk-tBZOGR2fmFfxbeGHA5VRvtkM7EBiAzs5kRsMRe0-BX4pt1RmyCtkQk3WzMY01bOQ5C6puAd4H2bwPTP4gFq9atLMe0wfV7PEGJXJUefe-jSfKiMHg6H6Or-P5hfiGYh7anYAwKTaWIgAzKdHo9bBsBt2mx-c1NGvTj1erXRZZ_EmTQf-V5sLPs2PsaQVLdcXQxbPrB43GKBXZh_9ry05K5m0U3LXmDyUoaeTwqOtk1RfbP9fEGUTFplTbACzwqYrCHnM7kjzB_J1doIXlrbQHTimAVRaXI2-FlBrFveOn9BGSxxZVAujq6vl97-IHw5exBiLmhW2XEO564Vx4X954RATXG1DUr6amk0sLFToxTUGJqLiRPzBMXuFiLrzstS7LFfOpI836IBIS4PT_W8Q6CNhHkqLkIvwer3N--8JW3aGlyR0MlgZxOe5FZIFcz6v-FqyARXk0FMY7tn2Z/gqyDKybK0_DtRuwU5nFpqXFB71v-7MUw/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="秘鲁投票结果势均力敌，左翼桑切斯领先"&gt;罗伯托·桑切斯(Roberto Sánchez)领先&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;现在注意力已经转移到国外，海外投票可能会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/1n-bEKOFyDx2Ak4PzeGOJm5mIHgEsxYYVpM_zgfNg7Yt-B-wSVTCo2YTCwHGPBsyYKUiAh5xCB5MPkTQ68Fk4EFDy6-X-Yc7skWEcJBZpIU2l3DMK3nN04jbM-cjRiyccc1KEypT-Q3fg4003GwzyMBKbkFtnMPyIbvSdOuC4n3j-XeM47A0RnI1UEOnEy-ozk6syDAUBIJfPlzk74LxXBkhGUna0yqnLCuVER-KwkolGxLAQ6X4_28XaFfUkqrTVCOdhgJdmdu8RIxvqAEumA-rEWtz0ly73LaPk5PZducEvIXrU5TxIMjQLJxJtH2iWNtPUEDYPAOUuGI41bWFJaC8_QrfpdxKQGxIGKwfYi_YeoiI1oESGkg0zF34rrzLsE6ToyQkrnTPLQP0XHGnM7c9rFjj7CwML66Cnc51PFLiULOm2s9CMRIKHUUV4sK2JcIHwBbbU1l8MDDkZhvpMuFm0IrvYNk53ncLjI6ijW19KdmaLznsplOK6vm9aZg9z8KNTmAsp48QtBaPJf9EjbspNDX6j6xsmNXuaxK4_KO7RIsZF88ecA/RmVYegN5nc7TaQz65C1Ww3l9CHMF2-CM/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="秘鲁侨民成为刀锋总统竞选中的决胜者"&gt;打破僵局&lt;/a&gt;，让藤森接任她自 2011 年以来一直追求的职位。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这可能是她&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/66w9Xh_gaakPi8aUV-j58c8FETH40GMhhfz2bZCjvOwlplowdGoURytpRsYFvPn20BhFbacjgbo4PWOByr6SQQoe45sHoeQNAZBCXmm7WSaX1nrXabNVO-JFyPjB6mv7g6C7yS5v_wFD09s9JyPWJtqZP7te5JbFgkZEPll--KvhKzdsLrWz6PW7zkJF-8I8_wp-HfL9F580qQDXyTLYa9jrPJhPZdthH_2XfmBneHx_Y7QmG9VNjiFbGlIhp_n_LYoRxsJYrE1kQWUwNc9rY8V2VGf8RLnLlLnWmn3A_QHMWA-hmRvutHl3Xtks673gJ7xM5r37rPTQ1ysgZulowy6W_QQ8Yv4OMn5j6sJt0FGM-Cdmv2WA1Zwe00lqAMskkYMmlzM3XjUi92kzGpOeiP9Tup3YIGagt1G4BWgOTkyGkZ2JEOY0cB6JYd0pk5YMuv8ndZA9ocHd139GLbuZQULPliFmtGjDMDvKxAMXovhli9FmScrMY5juNc1J3r5sNrl0wTaKIrblLRup8ye2IQwQyJhGl-duKDtqyR-Vd8qw/YHnmolT_uZF1KOW2Ll5LNh4U2iDbFkwo/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="藤森在秘鲁决选最后阶段以微弱优势领先"&gt;迄今为止最好的一次投篮&lt;/a&gt;。对于一个本世纪几乎每一位总统都被送上法庭或入狱的国家来说，这将是相当大的奖励，或者说是相当大的风险，她的父亲也在其中。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;然而所有这些悬念最终可能会被证明是徒劳的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;无论谁获胜，秘鲁的现状都不太可能改变。也没有与支离破碎但有影响力的国会发生冲突。由于缺乏立法支持，桑切斯将难以推动&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/HKXUCEcyN1EMttO0LCrcAPgOmK3vxlHSna1K6P3u2GsjB5LGvpyxjl7CbJmRTaWrJSSbcPYYvHhUxVGx8lAnl0UGmecc8iLkglHo9v1KSu11i4YkXVOgiGUvJcA62WEWcDjxZibFZqqyzauDsA6ekwPgHqtFc6DVdQ1bcLyDv_IzF5MltgnyPBAZ6zUC4m_7qIw2gnT-n5GSB1V1XA1cGqPR0maxg6VxxDFOquO4hyg6kyTT2OWGcmGlgEd6coxhxLdd0dx2I83XGRHTTU48INYr-fDuMOOSt54UzgRT-1ar4Bpu1f5QuJiF68dR4mBvFsTwY5P6axIxWFddPWz11Cg01QXtGczsSN2BaA_aiAUU3AazLdKSg9pWDOiAIAdialbuhg3oOJwIopw3osOX0OWSa8XGhENw0uPUDzxychdruhZBJyP3aWJLz18nPkMivkHuC1-UKzZfs6wg6zHJmsQdyJCvlujPRMaqM9_BQzwTfD42d6Bad-7dBGbX1x8l2dm7A6086DZpjwgFvG4C1IAbDrMnQBcEfQCKleEf8EMfyz-ecfvd2g/QruXa3zOG85xtyYLtnchT1fmMtJoRnsI/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="选民前往投票站，秘鲁的经济奇迹岌岌可危"&gt;令投资者担忧的改革&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;藤森还需要搭建桥梁，但她完成完整五年任期的机会更大，因为她的政党控制着国会中最大的集团，并且应该在新恢复的参议院中拥有足够的席位来帮助保护她。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;弹劾仍然是秘鲁难以驾驭的政治体系中的一个常态。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;不管怎样，对于秘鲁人来说，下一任总统的当选可能不如维拉德是否仍然留任更重要。&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;—&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mBLIS0vFBXkh0hwoTH1p7zX6Ioc0GPXo5vy3mttgNpkX0ykH06p_Pmu_Qif2KswM2zxAd4r2nf3hTMuZhF7WyXzlmFQJWwK9zm5TS0jhJhZLwSRYza_s6LCIshixmsirqXEBV-lTlMeb-sfuWdhG3Os8b6zb1ZI2EGjXWAyAErAhN8YUByMQ84jhyfjUVAXVVnuBDBATA8sHWV6JzBtbAIppT5thq5KpP4MkUGv9eCvUMQAXDIGRmATmMj8QFyDc_a3eXzV_uqukJNT9Ex1oBiyjgrPMSyT-mRehiVjtPIhXYEB0ZVjjazXo-oboYpR9LVjqWUDq_1OqqCkmC7fKWZgshmyXk2F4vArv8JaSuPHOCLSi9LKFUXGAsnKaRn4NU8stCDtBZzbnUYy81Cm6YhM2hCPcY_T4e4-7OfBeHLmhnQvOsvulC8e854bekb6Cn4E64mrnAImSxuKUN2-uxSvtm56636X0ZSKs4Q/zA-o_M0YcMqOU4bo51BXAIgFchi3h3S2/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="卡拉·萨蒙·罗斯 |彭博社"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;卡拉·萨蒙·罗斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2yocK5.ilxo/v11/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Keiko Fujimori, presidential candidate for the Popular Force party, during a closing campaign rally in Lima, Peru, on Thursday, June 4, 2026. Conservative candidate Fujimori holds a three percentage point lead over her leftist contender ahead of next Sunday&amp;amp;#39;s runoff, according to a poll, in what is expected to be a close race for the presidency of one of Latin America&amp;amp;#39;s most stable economies. Photographer: Sebastian Castaneda&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg " width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2026 年 6 月 4 日星期四，人民力量党总统候选人藤森惠子在秘鲁利马举行的闭幕式竞选集会上。根据一项民意调查，在下周日的决选之前，保守派候选人藤森领先左翼竞争者 3 个百分点，预计这将是拉丁美洲最稳定经济体之一的总统职位的一场势均力敌的角逐。摄影师：塞巴斯蒂安·卡斯塔尼达&amp;amp;#x2F;彭博社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxI